The paper discusses the acquisition and use of knowledge by intelligent agents, which is a core topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of intelligent agents to automate tasks for Internet Autonomous System administrators suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also mentions the issue of reliability, which is a concern in software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SI).
